name: Open !
tagline: A rambling discursive outlook - Yes, crazy !
body:
### Note of Thanks
According to Murphy, one must be thankful to invite more prosperity. He might be correct, but my intention to thank the people who are the motivating force is different. A sincere gratitude to my two little brothers. Thank you @importerror and @_stultus for pushing me to build my own website.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
